# KeyAuth-Style Licensing Panel — Detailed Project Specification

> Ye document aapke diye gaye requirements ko organize karke ek clean, developer-ready prompt/spec me convert karta hai. Isse aap directly Claude Code, ChatGPT, ya kisi bhi developer ko de sakte hain taaki wo poora system bana sake.

---

## 1. Project Overview

Ek **multi-role licensing/authentication panel** banana hai (jaisa KeyAuth ka hota hai — reference: `terminalx999.com`) jisme 3 tarah ke access levels honge:

- **Owner** — sabse powerful, poore system ka full control
- **Admin** — Owner jitna powerful, almost same permissions
- **Reseller** — limited access, sirf apne credits/packages ke hisaab se keys generate kar sakta hai

System ka use software licensing (keys generate karna, HWID lock karna, expiry set karna) ke liye hoga, saath me Discord bot integration bhi hoga jisse resellers apna khud ka bot bana kar keys generate kar sakein.

### 1.1 UI/UX Design Philosophy — Minimalism

Poore website (Landing Page + Dashboard, dono) ka design **minimalist** hona chahiye:

- **Clean layout** — bohot zyada elements/clutter avoid karna, sirf zaroori cheez screen par dikhe
- **Generous whitespace/spacing** — elements ke beech breathing room ho, cramped na lage
- **Limited color palette** — 1 background color (dark ya light — jo bhi choose karein) + 1 primary accent color (e.g. sirf ek subtle accent — green/blue) + neutral grays. Bohot saare bright/neon colors ek saath avoid karna
- **Simple typography** — ek clean sans-serif font (e.g. Inter, Geist, Manrope) — max 2 font weights use karna (regular + semi-bold/bold), bade decorative fonts avoid karna
- **Flat design** — heavy gradients, glow effects, drop shadows minimal rakhna; agar shadow chahiye to subtle/soft rakhna
- **Icons simple/outline style** — filled/3D icons avoid karna, thin-line icons use karna (e.g. Lucide icons)
- **Cards/borders subtle** — light border ya very soft background contrast se sections separate karna, heavy boxes/borders avoid karna
- **Micro-interactions minimal but smooth** — hover/transition effects simple aur subtle hone chahiye, flashy animations nahi

> Note: Pehle jo landing page ka "neon/cyberpunk glow" theme discuss hua tha, usko ab **minimalist version** me convert karna hai — structure (hero, features, how-it-works, footer) same rahega, lekin visual style clean/minimal hoga, heavy neon-glow effects ki jagah subtle accent color aur bohot saara whitespace use hoga.

