## 9. Reseller Creation Form (Owner/Admin side)

Jab Owner/Admin ek naya Reseller banata hai, form me ye fields honi chahiye:

1. Username / Password
2. Initial Credits (max 10,000, Owner ke liye "Infinite" option bhi)
3. Package Assignment (multi-select checkboxes)
4. Permission: "Allow this Reseller to create sub-Resellers" (Yes/No toggle)
5. Permission: "Allow API/Bot Access" (Yes/No toggle)
6. **App ID & Secret ID Option:**
   - Reseller create karte waqt ek option hoga: **"Generate New App ID/Secret"** ya **"Keep Existing App ID/Secret"**
   - Agar **New** select kiya jaye → system automatically fresh App ID + Secret Key generate karega us Reseller ke liye
   - Agar **Existing** select kiya jaye → jo App ID/Secret already system me set hai (default/shared) wahi is Reseller ko assign ho jayega
   - Ye App ID + Secret hi Reseller ke API/Bot system me use hote hain (Discord bot ya kisi bhi external integration ko authenticate karne ke liye)

