## 11. Suggested Tech Stack

- **Backend / Database:** **Supabase** (already set up — project name: **"keyauth"**). Poora backend (Auth, Database, Storage, Realtime) isi Supabase project ke andar hi store/manage hoga.
  - Supabase Auth ka use Owner/Admin/Reseller login ke liye (custom roles + RLS policies ke saath)
  - Supabase Postgres Database me saari tables (`users`, `packages`, `reseller_packages`, `keys`, `credit_logs`, `api_tokens` etc.) create hongi — Section 10 ka schema isi Supabase project me implement hoga
  - **Row Level Security (RLS)** zaroor enable karni hai taaki:
    - Reseller sirf apna hi data (apni keys, apne users, apna App ID/Secret) access kar sake
    - Owner hi sabka data (sab reseller/admin ka App ID/Secret) access kar sake
  - 2FA secret aur App ID/Secret jaisi sensitive fields ke liye extra RLS policy + encryption (agar possible ho) rakhni chahiye
- **Frontend:** React + Tailwind (sidebar dashboard layout), Supabase JS client (`@supabase/supabase-js`) se connect
- **Bot:** Discord.js (Node) ya discord.py (Python) — Supabase ke API/REST endpoints (ya Supabase Edge Functions) ke through key generate karega

