## 12. Landing Page

Panel ke backend/dashboard ke alawa ek **public Landing Page** bhi chahiye (jo login karne se pehle sabko dikhe) — style **terminalx999.com** jaisi (dark, cyberpunk/hacker-themed, "secure kernel/auth system" vibe).

### 12.1 Overall Theme
- **Minimalist design** (see Section 1.1) — clean background (dark ya light, aapki choice), ek subtle accent color, bohot saara whitespace
- Simple sans-serif typography, thin-line icons, flat cards with soft/light borders (heavy neon-glow effects nahi — bas ek subtle accent highlight use hoga CTA buttons/links par)
- Overall feel: professional, clean, "secure tech product" — clutter-free

### 12.2 Top Navbar
- Left: Site/Brand Logo + Name
- Right: **Login** button (leads to login page)

### 12.3 Hero Section
- Small version tag/badge (e.g. "V1.0 STABLE")
- Bada heading — product ka core value proposition (e.g. hardware-binding, encrypted licensing system)
