- Section heading (e.g. "Core Features")
- Grid of feature cards (3-4 columns) — har card me icon + short title + 1-2 line description
  - Example features: HWID/Hardware Binding, Encrypted Authentication, Reseller System, Discord Bot Integration, Real-time Dashboard, 2FA Security

### 12.5 "How It Works" Section
- Section heading
- 3 steps numbered format:
  1. Account/Key Generation
  2. Secure Authentication Handshake
  3. Instant Authorization/Access

### 12.6 Footer
- Brand name + short tagline
- Contact link (e.g. WhatsApp/Telegram/Discord support link)
- Column links: Platform (Dashboard, API, Bot), Resources (Docs, Status), Company (Terms, Privacy, Contact)

### 12.7 Tech Notes
- Landing page static/marketing hoga — koi sensitive data yahan render nahi hoga
- "Login" aur "Register/Get Started" buttons Owner/Admin/Reseller login page ki taraf redirect karenge
- Isi landing page ko React + Tailwind me banaya ja sakta hai (dashboard jaisa hi stack), lekin ye publicly accessible route hoga (no auth required)

