## 13. Important Notes

- Backend Supabase project **"keyauth"** me already login/setup ho chuka hai — naya backend project bana ke duplicate setup nahi karna, sab kuch isi existing Supabase project ke andar build karna hai.
- Har role ka access strictly server-side enforce hona chahiye (sirf UI se hide karna kaafi nahi — Supabase RLS policies + API level par bhi permission check zaroori hai).
- Credit deduction aur key creation **atomic transaction** me honi chahiye taaki race condition me double-spending na ho (Supabase Postgres functions/RPC ka use kiya ja sakta hai iske liye).
- Sensitive actions (Admin create, infinite credits assign, ban/unban) ke liye **audit log** rakhna recommended hai.

